PMS : Patient Management System

We'll use this application to accomplish the following

Front-end

1. Health practioner Login
2. Paitent's data entry by health practioner
3. Patient's follow-up's entries by Practioners
4. Track the paitent's details/Procedures/reports etc
5. Log the adverse events
6. Print the details


Back-end

1. Admin login
2. Add and manage health ppractioner's data
3. Add and Manage master data i.e Hospitals details etc
4. Generate Reports
5. Add Reverse Events